description.displayText: Laura is a true pleasure.  I know Laura for 14 years.  To see her grow into a mature adult is nothing less than a joy.  She is extremely kind, very easy to get along with.  She takes and accepts challenges and looks for positive ways to solve them.  Laura is also extremely dependable and trustworthy.  It allows an individual to know trust is there  when given a task at hand.
